NAME
    goscaffold - Create a project scaffold for your golang projects
SYNOPSIS
    goscaffold create-project github.com/apereg goscaffold [subcommands...]
DESCRIPTION
    goscaffold allow create a basic structrue for your golang projects, furthermore you can enable a basic pipeline gitlab and use your project with docker
        create-project:
            * The first argument will be the namespace of your application
            * The second argument is the application name
            --gitlabci With this argument the scaffold tool generate a minimum valid pipeline
            --workspace {workspace} if you not use the default workspace you can change with this argument
EXAMPLES
    The following example show how to implement all options for the tool:
        goscaffold create-project github.com/aperezg goscaffold --workspace $GOPATH/other/src --gitlabci --docker
AUTHOR
